The paper focuses on the problem of generalization in deep reinforcement learning, which is a core topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper deals with robotics (cs.RO) and computer vision (cs.CV) tasks, which are common applications of deep RL. Finally, the paper also discusses the problem of system changes at test time, which is related to control systems (cs.SY).
